CustomField.description: ID of the Google Docs template for document creation. When looking at a Google Doc URL, the ID is the long string of numbers and letters found between "document/d/" and "/edit". Don't forget to set its Share settings to "Anyone with link: Can Edit"

CustomField.label: GDoc Template Document ID
